33. use WITH ROLLUP to calc total
Syntax:

SELECT 
    c1, c2, aggregate_function(c3)
FROM
    table_name
GROUP BY c1, c2 WITH ROLLUP;

example:

select coalesce(job,'TOTAL') job,
 sum(sal) sal
 from emp
 group by job with rollup



32. paging :  OFFSET... FETCH ...

SELECT ...
ORDER BY ...
OFFSET n ROWS 
FETCH NEXT n ROWS ONLY

